{"tid":2269025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中印衝突勝負已分？印度失掉300平方公里「爭議山區」","createTime":"2020-11-03T08:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T13:59:33.000Z","uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc273a916d1e5e4bc4de8eb10f7918e8b760842","tid":2269025,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"中國印度年中爆發邊境流血衝突以來，關係持續緊張，中印兩軍至今仍在對峙，準備在高原上捱住嚴寒過冬。中國印度本輪衝突烈度多年罕見之餘，走向亦見苗頭。有印度官員坦言，印度至今已失去近300平方公里「爭議山區」的控制。這大小相當於5個美國紐約曼哈頓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭博社引述多名印度知情官員報道，中印衝突過去6個月以來實際上重劃了戰線，印度在中印邊境西段達普桑盤地（Depsang Plains）一帶，失去了約250平方公里地域的控制，並同時在班公錯（Pangong Tso；班公湖）失去了50平方公里地域的控制權。"},{"pid":"1ea63dc81f5b3e3243d7e1a237980354cfcadc13","tid":2269025,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"應該同你個名一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3df316fcaad6ec879b8625071779064e37991a","tid":2269025,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"打未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f86338e269111e4ca0dc5216e383e1647b47c60","tid":2269025,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:16:16.000Z","msg":"點解印度咁多人又有西藏人幫拖都會輸番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1634c933b836402d8a3f8fe9ac0a93f9f676fe7e","tid":2269025,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"彭博社引述多名印度知情官員報道<br />\n<br />\n留名等fc <br />\n特別中共非常喜歡出口轉內銷<br />\n<br />\n彭博更係出名支那大好友"},{"pid":"6d0866d3d7002d5a3e606a8f10b25fed33f22ceb","tid":2269025,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"Bloomberg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶共架~"},